headline: Occidental Petroleum: Getting Close To An Upgrade
summary: Occidental Petroleum remains a 'hold' due to valuation concerns despite increased guidance and improved debt reduction efforts following the CrownRock acquisition. Read more here.

headline: Dodge & Cox Balanced Fund Q4 2024 Shareholder Letter
summary: The S&P 500 Index rose by 26.3% in 2023 and posted a 25.0% return in 2024, marking its largest consecutive annual gains since 1998. Read more here.
